{"tid":1718824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到有人JR］做特務警犬咁開心呀嗱，唔該議員JR攞番佢哋間懲教宿舍！","createTime":"2019-11-14T02:49:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:28:51.000Z","uid":322359,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"03bf80630c750741307bb70fdbcb4203d519e7ae","tid":1718824,"uid":322359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"柒婆依家要任命懲教人員做特務警犬，即係佢哋要暫時放棄咗懲教嘅識務。成班藍絲鎖匙佬自動請纓去打人又有OT賺，本身啲工作屎就要其他同事食番，公平咩？！既然轉咗身份做特務警犬，仲符合資格住懲教宿舍咩？！<br />\n<br />\n議員請快快手去JR佢哋個懲教宿舍資格(EO同律師朋友都話好大機會贏)，拎番佢哋間宿舍等佢哋變condom又要訓街！！！等佢哋知道助紂為虐嘅後果！！！以後冇人敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足請幫推，P牌推唔郁，無限感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56a8761cb7262e770ba1044d207b1a8376f276e","tid":1718824,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"試下又唔會死"},{"pid":"eb9101a45d66f7d04732475016f51a57cbc261b5","tid":1718824,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T02:52:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">連登嘅冷氣軍師，想幫手又冇得發夢嘅，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔該幫手上Twitter，Reddit幫手！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">前線搏晒老命同班警甴對抗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">你哋唔係連撳幾個掣都懶呀嘛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Retweet + Like + Reply</span></span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n美國議員繼續為香港發聲，大家快啲去回應支持啦～<br />\n<br />\n！！！提出法案嘅Marco Rubio話有好消息！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=99c8451f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1194749198345949187&h=c1718001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1194749198345949187</a><br />\n<br />\n！！！Dick Durbin促請Leader McConnell 就法案進行投票！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=4e018800\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorDurbin%2Fstatus%2F1194708875972349953&h=47d24cbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorDurbin/status/1194708875972349953</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Marsha Blackburn 繼續撐香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=ac8538e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMarshaBlackburn%2Fstatus%2F1194798820695138310%3Fs%3D09&h=56d542bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/MarshaBlackburn/status/1194798820695138310?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n！！Rick Scott鬧黨媒冷血<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1194622539017752576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1194622539017752576&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZBZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=5dce60d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1194622539017752576&h=2e6ec6ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1194622539017752576</a><br />\n<br />\n！！眾議院Jim McGovern話唔好各打五十大板<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcGovern/status/1194627617913069570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcGovern%2Fstatus%2F1194627617913069570&d=Ue9aQsdn